                $2199
            </h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div
    class='price-box price-box-ultra'>
    <div
        class='bg'>
    </div>
    <div
        class='details'>
        <h1
            class='mt-5'>
            Ultra
        </h1>
        <p>
            Have you been on your feet for a long time? Then this option is yours.
